==English==
===Noun===
'''nicotine'''
{{wikipedia}}

#(Chemistry) An [[alkaloid]] (C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>14</sub>N<sub>2</sub>), commonly occurring in the [[tobacco]] plant.  In small doses it is a [[habit-forming]] [[stimulant]], in larger doses it is [[toxic]] and is often used in [[insecticide]]s.  It is a [[carcinogen]].